<h2 id="50">5. Editing a board</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>When opening the menu <strong>Start » Boards</strong>, you see the number of cards and columns, the name of the board as well as the time period of the last change on every card that you created. Click on <strong>Rename board</strong> to enter a new name for the board. Click on <strong>Delete board</strong> to delete the board.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>In order to edit boards, click on the name of the board. You can add new columns and cards and edit the cards. Pay attention to the information given in <a href="#table-boards-edit-card">Table 1</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
